column1: Five year average weekly deaths by sex and age group, England and Wales, deaths that occurred between 2015 and 2019 1,2,3,4
2 Figures based on boundaries as of February 2020.

3 Figures are for deaths occurring between 2015 and 2019. Figures only include deaths that were registered by 29 February 2020, so figures for 2019 may be an underestimate due to registration delays. More information on registration delays for a range of causes can be found on the ONS website via the link below.
Impact of registration delays on mortality statistics in England and Wales: 2018 (latest)
4 Each week is the five year average number of deaths of that week over the years 2015 to 2019.
